---
title: Chicken Thigh Schnitzel Plates with Dill-Garlic Smashed Potatoes and Apple Slaw
description: Comfort food at its finest! Our chicken schnitzel recipe has all the fixings you want, with herby smashed potatoes, crisp and bright apple slaw and the creamy zip of Dijonnaise to bring it all together!
